  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003csection\u003e\n        \n\n    \n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003eWe\u0026#39;ve said it once, and we\u0026#39;ll say it again: Don\u0026#39;t mess with retail employees. Really, don\u0026#39;t mess with any customer-facing employee. But retail employees are one of the roughest and toughest workers that will dish you some of the gnarliest revenge with a smile on their face. You won\u0026#39;t even know what hit ya until days later, sometimes years! \u003ca href=\"https://cheezburger.com/40684293/friend-gets-ignored-by-server-due-to-his-sobriety-so-friends-leave-0-tip-on-a-300-tab-service\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003eIt\u0026#39;s a foolish thing to have so much entitlement that you think you can get away with treating people like they aren\u0026#39;t humans\u003c/a\u003e simply because they have a job that \u0026#34;serves\u0026#34; you. Gross. Cancelled. Go away. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eTake, for example, \u003ca href=\"https://www.reddit.com/r/pettyrevenge/comments/1kpb06s/got_revenge_and_theyll_never_know/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003ethis\u003c/a\u003e retail employee from the late \u0026#39;70s. He worked at a fancy jewelry store and got epic revenge on a snoot couple who came in to purchase an expensive wedding gift. \u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n\n    \u003cli\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe couple were your classic Karens. They acted entitled and condescending to an employee who was being nothing buy helpful and kind to them. So once the couple purchased the gift for a price that is currently equivalent to $500-700 today, the retail employee devised his plan. Though the entitled customers put down a pretty penny for the gift, they now were made to look like total cheapskates after this retail employee got his revenge. See for yourself below! \u003c/p\u003e\n\n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10508529920/h8AC17260/50-18\" id=\"_r_a_10508529920\" width=\"800\" height=\"420\" alt=\"$50 $18\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n            \u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ci\u003e\u003csub\u003e\u003csup\u003eThe image does not depict the actual subjects of the story. Subjects are models.\u003c/sup\u003e\u003c/sub\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e \u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\n                                    \u003ch2\u003e\u0026#34;Got revenge and they\u0026#39;ll never know\u0026#34;\u003c/h2\u003e\n            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10508537344/h282E9959/this-many-years-ago-retail-sales-person-jewelry-store-shopping-mall-really-happened-favorite-memory\" id=\"_r_a_10508537344\" width=\"800\" height=\"866\" alt=\"This from many years ago when I was a retail sales person in a jewelry store in a shopping mall. Really happened, a favorite memory.\" title=\"\u0026#34;Got revenge and they\u0026#39;ll never know\u0026#34;\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10508536832/hA9086BB6/earshot-during-most-transaction-which-took-long-time-and-featured-husband-being-aj-jerry-whole-time\" id=\"_r_a_10508536832\" width=\"800\" height=\"945\" alt=\"Our assistant manager, let\u0026#39;s call him \u0026#34;Jerry,\u0026#34; sold a fancy crystal decanter set to a couple who was going to give it as a wedding gift. I was within earshot during most of the transaction, which took a long time and featured the husband being aj to Jerry the whole time.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10508536320/h984689F4/jerry-totally-professional-kept-his-cool-remained-cheerful-and-obliging-through-all-ab-e-at-end\" id=\"_r_a_10508536320\" width=\"800\" height=\"767\" alt=\"Condescending, demanding, demeaning, the whole works. Jerry was totally professional, kept his cool, remained cheerful and obliging through all the ab e. At the end of the\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10508537088/hC0DA86D2/did-spectacular-wrapping-job-went-all-out-with-luxury-ribbon-silver-metallic-textured-paper-works\" id=\"_r_a_10508537088\" width=\"800\" height=\"960\" alt=\"transaction, he asked if they would like complimentary gift wrapping. Customer agreed, Jerry took the box into the back room and did a spectacular wrapping job. Went all out with luxury ribbon, silver metallic textured paper, the works.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10508537600/h6D869644/asked-why-he-so-cheerful-after-experience-jerry-said-oh-s-fine-and-held-up-price-tag-g-and-smiled\" id=\"_r_a_10508537600\" width=\"800\" height=\"807\" alt=\"Customers left, Jerry smiled and waved goodbye. When they were gone he was still smiling and I asked why he was so cheerful after that experience? Jerry said, \u0026#34;oh it\u0026#39;s fine\u0026#34; and held up the price tag g in and smiled.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10508536576/h26149FA7/jerry-had-removed-original-price-tag-there-one-price-whole-set-but-then-stuck-new-ones-on-bottoms\" id=\"_r_a_10508536576\" width=\"800\" height=\"875\" alt=\"The decanter set had cost around $150 (this was 1978 so maybe $500 in today\u0026#39;s dollars?) While in the back room wrapping the gift, Jerry had removed the original price tag (there was one price for the whole set), but then stuck new ones on the bottoms\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10508537856/hB4A2F67E/wrapped-them-all-nice-and-pretty-he-said-and-beauty-is-theyll-never-know-and-gave-satisfied-laugh\" id=\"_r_a_10508537856\" width=\"800\" height=\"788\" alt=\"of each piece, something like $17.77 on the decanter, and $3.77 on each glass. Then wrapped them all nice and pretty. He said \u0026#34;And the beauty of it is, they\u0026#39;ll never know!\u0026#34; And gave a satisfied laugh.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10508538880/h15A2923A/d-cartier-juwel-kohlmarkt-brillanten-import-junvel-perlen-import-firma-maxmara-s\" id=\"_r_a_10508538880\" width=\"800\" height=\"1204\" alt=\"D Cartier Juwel KOHLMARKT BRILLANTEN IMPORT Junvel PERLEN-IMPORT FIRMA MaxMara s\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n            \u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ci\u003e\u003csub\u003e\u003csup\u003eThe image does not depict the actual subjects of the story. Subjects are models.\u003c/sup\u003e\u003c/sub\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10508551680/hF97D667A/coderjoe1-making-as-ole-look-like-cheap-as-ole\" id=\"_r_a_10508551680\" width=\"800\" height=\"872\" alt=\"CoderJoe1 Making the as ole look like a cheap as ole\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10508552960/h7AE15A25/saved-last-like-icing-on-cake-77-on-all-prices-characteristic-practice-local-kmart-stores-at-time\" id=\"_r_a_10508552960\" width=\"800\" height=\"612\" alt=\"CCR76 OP Yes! Jerry took particular glee in the individual tags. When he described to us what he had done, he saved that for last, like the icing on the cake. The .77 on all the prices was a characteristic practice of the local Kmart stores at the time.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10508553472/h4003C9F8/striptorn-k-mart-red-light-special-crystal-lol\" id=\"_r_a_10508553472\" width=\"800\" height=\"763\" alt=\"striptorn K-Mart red light special crystal LOL.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10508554240/hE817681A/bought-as-set-but-simply-assembled-repeated-items-which-adds-even-more-atmosphere-cheapness-fine\" id=\"_r_a_10508554240\" width=\"800\" height=\"654\" alt=\"LDESAD This pettiness covers two purposes - first, it will be very annoying to peel off these price tags from each item, and second, it creates the illusion that these items were not bought as a set, but simply assembled from repeated items, which adds even more atmosphere of cheapness. Fine.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10508559616/hDBF53B21/financial_refugee-is-5-star-karma-dished-out-with-smile\" id=\"_r_a_10508559616\" width=\"800\" height=\"704\" alt=\"financial_refugee That is 5 star karma dished out with a smile\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10508560384/hCF7164A2/if-reddit-had-been-thing-back-then-aita-not-acting-grateful-enough-cheap-wedding-gift-my-laws\" id=\"_r_a_10508560384\" width=\"800\" height=\"622\" alt=\"PinkyLizardBrains If Reddit had been a thing back then: \u0026#34;AITA for not acting \u0026#39;grateful enough\u0